{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But for some reason, this Friday I want-- I somehow, for no particular reason, want to get out of there, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't-- so 10 minutes after I left, one of these rockets hit a direct hit on the bathhouse and everybody, maybe a couple hundred people, killed instantaneously, the staff and all these people taking these-- [INAUDIBLE] there were several hundred bathtubs on many floors, you know-- were killed immediately.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so that was-- was 10 minutes before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For some reason-- I don't know why I left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would have stayed longer normally, maybe another half an hour, hung around and splashed around and you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was only a kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I was only 15 years old, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- And these are my memories of-- but I had good memories of London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a good time-- I-- in the boys club and going to school at night and stimulation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I worked and worked with good people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and in those days, a lot of Jews were-- were maybe even Communist-oriented working people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In those days, back in the Second World War, before people came out of Russia, people thought not that Israel was a country, but that-- that the paradise was-- the Messianic Age was in Russia.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was all ideology.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- at lunchtime, the workmen got together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I joined the union.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I was 15 years old, I joined the union.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had a special political meeting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I joined that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and there were people trying to influence me to join the Junior Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
